{"type": "article", "id": 30479, "title": "香薰盐灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-02T23:04:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 30, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160802220440qWP7ziS9t4wgr85I.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>要用一句话形容这款名为 <a href=\"http://thezencube.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Zencube</a> 的盐灯，用 LIFE Home 的那句“方块里的自然”或许再合适不过：作为世界上第一款智能盐灯，它将来自喜马拉雅的水晶盐与最新的科技结合在了一起。你可以通过配套的应用任意调节盐灯的颜色，让它变成一盏气氛灯。不吝啬于展现水晶盐的美丽，LIFE Home 专门设计了半开放式的防水外壳，顶部则留有一个精油槽方便你利用独特的香味净化空气。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/zencube-the-coolest-healthiest-smart-lamp--2#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 129 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802220451yLVkR6YEhjUOusti.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.475806\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802220451UlrN46c712OeGfZM.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802220451CNLiD76ysJEWq1Pr.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.679032\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160802220451QKeUDfPBnwkWmLMp.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.679032\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}